#: ../development/controllers.rst:122
msgid "PDF and CSV controllers"
msgstr "Contrôleurs PDF et CSV"

#: ../development/controllers.rst:124
msgid ""
"The ``PdfController`` and ``CsvController`` in Galette centralize all "
"PDF/CSV outputs, but the most interesting point is the ``sendResponse`` "
"method that set correct headers and contents for those specific outputs."
msgstr ""
"Les classe ``PdfController`` et ``CsvController`` dans Galette centralisent "
"toutes les sorties PDF/CSV, mais la partie la plus intéressante est la "
"méthode ``sendResponse`` qui place correctement les en-têtes et contenus "
"pour ces sorties spécifiques."

#: ../development/controllers.rst:126
msgid ""
"The ``PdfController::sendResponse`` method waits for a "
"``Slim\\Http\\Response`` and a ``Galette\\IO\\Pdf`` objects to work."
msgstr ""
"La méthode ``PdfController::sendResponse`` attend un objet "
"``Slim\\Http\\Response`` et un ``Galette\\IO\\Pdf`` pour fonctionner."

#: ../development/controllers.rst:128
msgid ""
"The ``CsvController::sendResponse`` method waits for a "
"``Slim\\Http\\Response``, path to the file on disk, and file name for "
"download."
msgstr ""
"La méthode ``CsvController::sendResponse`` attend un objet "
"``Slim\\Http\\Response``, le chemin sur le disques, et le nom du fichier "
"pour le téléchargement."

